description:
Season: 20
Original Air Date: 1/23/2007

Arthur Harrison arrives for his meeting with Brooke and Ridge. They inform him of their engagement and he agrees to carry Forrester Originals new fashion line. Brooke and Ridge celebrate the deal. Brooke tells Ridge she doesn’t want their feud with Nick to get ugly. Nick wants to get to know Taylor better and invites her to lunch at Chuck’s. While they are eating Nick gets a phone call from Arthur and must go meet him right away. They depart and Taylor accidentally leaves her sunglasses behind. Arthur is shocked when Nick offers to buy his company. Phoebe demands to know of Taylor what is going on between her and Nick.
